## ğŸš€ Features

### ğŸ‘¤ Authentication
- Student & Admin login using JWT
- Secure password hashing
- Role-based access control

### ğŸ“š Books Management
- View all available books
- Book quantity management
- Issue book (student)
- Return book with status update

### ğŸ” Issue & Return System
- Track issued books per user
- Auto issue date & due date logic
- Fine-ready structure (future enhancement)

### ğŸŒ Deployment Ready
- Backend deployed on **Render**
- Database hosted on **MongoDB Atlas**
- Environment variables securely managed

